# **CODE**
Phแบงn nรy tรดi sแบฝ `mรด phแปng` lแบกi thuแบญt toรกn `Bubble Sort` bแบฑng `Python` ๐ค๐ค๐ค


```python

def bubble_sort(arr: list) ->list:

  # i ฤแบกi diแปn cho vแป trรญ nแปi bแปt lรชn
  for i in range(n - 1, 0 , -1):

      if arr[j] > arr[j + 1]:
        arr[j], arr[j + 1] = arr[j + 1], arr[j]

  return arr
```
